---
description: Messaging and CRM integration rules
globs:
  - "apps/api/**/integrations/**"
  - "apps/worker/**/integrations/**"
  - "packages/contracts/**"
alwaysApply: false
---

Use official APIs only.

Before implementation:
- verify current official docs;
- record verification date;
- document permissions, review requirements, limits, pricing implications, and history constraints.

Implement signature verification, idempotency, quick acknowledgement, asynchronous processing, retries, dead-letter handling, token revocation, health, and reconciliation.

Never assume universal historical access.
Never use browser scraping or account impersonation.
